<P>&startq;Like her!&endq; he repeated, when able to &s;peak;
<PB N="302" REF="103">
&startq;why the old gentleman doats! He can never, el&s;e,
&s;eriou&s;ly &s;uppo&s;e I'll marry her.&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;He! he! he! yes, but he does, indeed, brother.
He's got every thing ready.&endq;</P>
<P>&startq;Has he, faith?&endq; cried Lynmere, again rolling on
